</p><p>我觉得这个世界上已经没有好男人了，或许是我没遇到吗？这种现象可不好，有哪个男人会觉得这个世界上已经没有好女人了吗？</p><p>睡觉去，祝愿自己做个好梦，嘻嘻，好像真的很久没做梦了...</p></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div><div class="content-main-box"><div class="contentbox"><div class="title"><div><a href="javascript:void(0)">紫棠</a> 发表于 2012-07-12 22:31:44</div><h1>抄书</h1></div><div class="details"><p>今天心血来潮开始抄书。找了个小笔记本子，满怀喜悦。居然下笔时还有点儿紧张。都说字如其人，虽说未必如此但可以分析。</p>
<p>可能是抄的比较崇拜的人的书吧，心情紧张而认真，一撇一捺写的不好都感到惋惜，但本来字就不好，惋惜满篇。虽说是崇拜的人但看他写的书又似懂非懂，而又赖以启蒙，不免矛盾心急。</p>
<p>今天抄的是黄元御的四圣心源。抄时写繁体字，顺便学繁体字。汉字只应该是繁体字。</p></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div><div class="content-main-box"><div class="contentbox"><div class="title"><div><a href="javascript:void(0)">虚无</a> 发表于 2012-07-12 22:00:25</div><h1>葫芦娃洗头发的时候，摘不摘头上的小葫芦？</h1></div><div class="details"><p>问：葫芦娃洗头发的时候，摘不摘头上的小葫芦？<br> 答：当然摘了！这是为什么呢？？因为葫芦里面装的是洗发水...</p></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div><div class="content-main-box"><div class="contentbox"><div class="title"><div><a href="javascript:void(0)">番茄炒鸡蛋</a> 发表于 2012-07-12 21:50:39</div><h1>亲爱，你要幸福</h1></div><div class="details"><p>闺蜜要结婚了。她说：亲爱，他很温柔。我说：那很好。她说：他很会照顾人。我说：真的不错。她说：他很爱我。我说：你很幸福。婚礼上，我看见了新郎，是他，那个追了我5年的男人。闺蜜俯在我耳朵说：亲爱，你要幸福！他很好，你却不要，对不起，我把他收留了。</p></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div><div class="content-main-box"><div class="contentbox"><div class="title"><div><a href="javascript:void(0)">如梦</a> 发表于 2012-07-12 18:19:03</div><h1>You belong to me</h1></div><div class="details"><p>See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise on a tropic isle<br> Just remember darling all the while<br> You belong to me<br> <br> See the Pyramids along the Nile<br> Watch the sun rise